{
  "video_id": "KqULHxlySi8",
  "title": "How To Create An Award-Winning Netflix Documentary w/ Matt D'Avella",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 4040.0,
      "end_time": 5460.0,
      "text": "- Matt D'Avella is the award-winning"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5460.0,
      "end_time": 8010.0,
      "text": "director of the documentary Minimalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 8010.0,
      "end_time": 9140.0,
      "text": "It's on Netflix."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9140.0,
      "end_time": 11760.0,
      "text": "It features some guests we've\nhad on the podcast in the past"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11760.0,
      "end_time": 14670.0,
      "text": "like Colin Wright and we\nhad Matt on the podcast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14670.0,
      "end_time": 15830.0,
      "text": "so that's what this video is about."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15830.0,
      "end_time": 17660.0,
      "text": "So, in today's video I wanna run"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17660.0,
      "end_time": 20420.0,
      "text": "through the best of that podcast episode."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20420.0,
      "end_time": 23410.0,
      "text": "Here is my conversation\nwith Matt D'Avella."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 23410.0,
      "end_time": 26420.0,
      "text": "First we talked about how\nMatt created Minimalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 26420.0,
      "end_time": 28120.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] Yeah, it just\nstarted out with, you know"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 28120.0,
      "end_time": 29970.0,
      "text": "let's just start filming\nas much as we can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29970.0,
      "end_time": 33124.0,
      "text": "let's explore this idea of\nminimalism and simple living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 33124.0,
      "end_time": 36366.0,
      "text": "and let's see how far\nwe can take this thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36366.0,
      "end_time": 39230.0,
      "text": "And then, we went through\nmany many iterations"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 39230.0,
      "end_time": 41810.0,
      "text": "and many versions of\nthe film before we were"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 41810.0,
      "end_time": 45780.0,
      "text": "finally, you know had something\nwe thought we were confident"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 45780.0,
      "end_time": 48860.0,
      "text": "that would be received well\nand that we were proud of."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48860.0,
      "end_time": 50400.0,
      "text": "- Then I wanted to talk about marketing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 50400.0,
      "end_time": 51610.0,
      "text": "so we talked about how to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 51610.0,
      "end_time": 54600.0,
      "text": "an initial sales bump in iTunes."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 54600.0,
      "end_time": 56880.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] I would say the one big thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 56880.0,
      "end_time": 59240.0,
      "text": "and the one big takeaway\nI have from a distribution"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 59240.0,
      "end_time": 62430.0,
      "text": "was having an audience going"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 62430.0,
      "end_time": 65040.0,
      "text": "into distribution is incredibly helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 65040.00000000001,
      "end_time": 68140.0,
      "text": "And so, two of the\nproducers who are also in"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 68140.0,
      "end_time": 70380.0,
      "text": "the film are Josh and Ryan from a website"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 70380.0,
      "end_time": 72200.0,
      "text": "called The Minimalists.com"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 72200.0,
      "end_time": 73970.0,
      "text": "And they have built up that website"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 73970.0,
      "end_time": 76123.0,
      "text": "at the point of the release of the film"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 76123.0,
      "end_time": 78610.0,
      "text": "to probably a few million people a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 78610.0,
      "end_time": 80850.0,
      "text": "that would go to their website."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 80850.0,
      "end_time": 83410.0,
      "text": "- We talked about how to\ncreate a watchable film."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 83410.0,
      "end_time": 85710.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] I mean that is\nreally like at its core"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 85710.0,
      "end_time": 87920.0,
      "text": "a big part of making a good film."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 87920.0,
      "end_time": 89750.0,
      "text": "Is it watchable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 89750.0,
      "end_time": 90710.0,
      "text": "Is it engaging?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 90710.0,
      "end_time": 92300.0,
      "text": "Does it pull you through?"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 92300.0,
      "end_time": 94850.0,
      "text": "And I, you know that now everybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 94850.0,
      "end_time": 97010.0,
      "text": "can make a documentary, and people"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 97010.0,
      "end_time": 99250.0,
      "text": "that don't have a ton\nof experience with it"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 99250.0,
      "end_time": 100870.0,
      "text": "are getting into it,\nwhich I think is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 100870.0,
      "end_time": 103530.0,
      "text": "Like yeah sure, I encourage people"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 103530.0,
      "end_time": 105380.0,
      "text": "to try to pursue this if it's something"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 105380.0,
      "end_time": 106946.0,
      "text": "that they're really passionate about."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 106946.0,
      "end_time": 110529.0,
      "text": "But, I also come into it\nwith like 10 to 15 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 110529.0,
      "end_time": 112030.0,
      "text": "of experience as a filmmaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 112030.0,
      "end_time": 114130.0,
      "text": "so I kinda knew news story telling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 114130.0,
      "end_time": 116626.0,
      "text": "not on a large scale\nlike a feature like film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 116626.0,
      "end_time": 119870.0,
      "text": "but I kind of had a pretty\ngood intuition about how"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 119870.0,
      "end_time": 123080.0,
      "text": "to carry somebody through a\nstory, which is that's key."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 123080.0,
      "end_time": 124920.0,
      "text": "- What to look for in the first cut."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 124920.0,
      "end_time": 127170.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] Yeah, so I know\nfor a lot of filmmakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 127170.0,
      "end_time": 130310.0,
      "text": "a lot of editors, and I\nedited the the film myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 130310.0,
      "end_time": 132840.0,
      "text": "The beginning, the first\ncut, the very first"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 132840.0,
      "end_time": 135250.0,
      "text": "rough cut is usually\nso rough that it's like"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 135250.0,
      "end_time": 137180.0,
      "text": "embarrassing and like\nyou wouldn't want anybody"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 137180.0,
      "end_time": 139030.0,
      "text": "else to see it, and I've\nworked with some editors"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 139030.0,
      "end_time": 141540.0,
      "text": "before and I've talked with\nothers who've done well."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 141540.0,
      "end_time": 143410.0,
      "text": "It's usually how it is; is like"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 143410.0,
      "end_time": 146330.0,
      "text": "because when you're\nworking on a feature film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 146330.0,
      "end_time": 147300.0,
      "text": "when you're working on something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 147300.0,
      "end_time": 149663.0,
      "text": "either has funding or\nproducers or partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 149663.0,
      "end_time": 152480.0,
      "text": "you need to get everybody's\ninput and feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 152480.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "and you need to make sure\nthe vision is cohesive"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 160050.0,
      "text": "and everybody's onboard with\nwhere the film is being taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 160050.0,
      "end_time": 162740.0,
      "text": "- How not to lose your\nstory in the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 162740.0,
      "end_time": 165530.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] The best advice I\never got was if your story"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 165530.0,
      "end_time": 167510.0,
      "text": "doesn't change along the\nway, you're not listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 167510.0,
      "end_time": 170380.0,
      "text": "And I think that's mainly\ntrue for a documentary"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 170380.0,
      "end_time": 173606.0,
      "text": "but I'm sure that's true\nfor narrative films as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 173606.0,
      "end_time": 177360.0,
      "text": "where you may have to\nchange things in the moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 177360.0,
      "end_time": 180890.0,
      "text": "you know you may have a\nwhole idea of how this shoot"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 180890.0,
      "end_time": 181723.0,
      "text": "is gonna play out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 181723.0,
      "end_time": 183050.0,
      "text": "the entire script, and then when you get"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 183050.0,
      "end_time": 184473.0,
      "text": "to the location you realize oh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184473.0,
      "end_time": 186380.0,
      "text": "the lighting's not working,\nthis isn't working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 186380.0,
      "end_time": 188220.0,
      "text": "the actor isn't feeling it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 188220.0,
      "end_time": 190680.0,
      "text": "And you have to make changes on the fly."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 190680.0,
      "end_time": 192860.0,
      "text": "It's very much true for a documentary."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 192860.0,
      "end_time": 193970.0,
      "text": "- Then we talked funding."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 193970.0,
      "end_time": 197400.0,
      "text": "How did he get the money to\ncreate the movie Minimalism?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 197400.0,
      "end_time": 198803.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] We funded it ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 198803.0,
      "end_time": 202480.0,
      "text": "So, we didn't..."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 202480.0,
      "end_time": 206193.0,
      "text": "Going into this film they\nhad a decent audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 207440.0,
      "end_time": 211400.0,
      "text": "but we weren't proven filmmakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 211400.0,
      "end_time": 213770.0,
      "text": "And to get a budget for a film"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 214900.0,
      "end_time": 216240.0,
      "text": "it's little bit more challenging"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 216240.0,
      "end_time": 218097.0,
      "text": "that obviously takes a lot of groundwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 218097.0,
      "end_time": 220250.0,
      "text": "But honestly I didn't think we needed it"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 220250.0,
      "end_time": 223930.0,
      "text": "because going into it I\nhad the filmmaking skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 223930.0,
      "end_time": 225660.0,
      "text": "to actually produce and make it"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 225660.0,
      "end_time": 227770.0,
      "text": "and I was confident that I could do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 227770.0,
      "end_time": 232120.0,
      "text": "And Josh and Ryan had connections\nwithin this community."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 232120.0,
      "end_time": 234470.0,
      "text": "They were able to setup interviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 234470.0,
      "end_time": 236850.0,
      "text": "and down the road they were the ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 236850.0,
      "end_time": 239900.0,
      "text": "that helped with the major\npush at the distribution."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 239900.0,
      "end_time": 242780.0,
      "text": "So, we were like all right let's just kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 242780.0,
      "end_time": 246560.0,
      "text": "of pull our money together\nand go bit by bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 246560.0,
      "end_time": 248230.0,
      "text": "- We talked from a marketing point of view"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 248230.0,
      "end_time": 251470.0,
      "text": "the release strategy for\nthe movie Minimalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 251470.0,
      "end_time": 253350.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] Yeah, so the\nfirst thing was actually"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 253350.0,
      "end_time": 256250.0,
      "text": "we did a month long release on Vimeo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 256250.0,
      "end_time": 259570.0,
      "text": "which for no real reason but to make it"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 259570.0,
      "end_time": 261400.0,
      "text": "very simple and have one place to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 261399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 263050.0,
      "text": "We'd never done this before."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 263050.0,
      "end_time": 264330.0,
      "text": "We didn't know about how to even"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 264330.0,
      "end_time": 266650.0,
      "text": "put it on iTunes or go about any of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 266650.0,
      "end_time": 269200.0,
      "text": "and Vimeo just seemed like\nthe easiest way to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 269200.0,
      "end_time": 271170.0,
      "text": "And in hindsight, I think\nwe would have attempted"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 271170.0,
      "end_time": 273610.0,
      "text": "to try to get connections\nfirst and then like"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 273610.0,
      "end_time": 275500.0,
      "text": "contact Vimeo and say,\nhey, we're planning on"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 275500.0,
      "end_time": 276590.0,
      "text": "doing a limited release."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 276590.0,
      "end_time": 278620.0,
      "text": "This is our audience size."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 278620.0,
      "end_time": 280300.0,
      "text": "We expect it to be pretty good."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 280300.0,
      "end_time": 283710.0,
      "text": "Can you give us any kind\nof additional promotion?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 283710.0,
      "end_time": 285670.0,
      "text": "Like could you like put\nus on the homepage banner?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 285670.0,
      "end_time": 289009.0,
      "text": "Or give us a cut in terms of how much"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 289009.0,
      "end_time": 290490.0,
      "text": "you'll be taking away."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 290490.0,
      "end_time": 292870.0,
      "text": "In turn giving them exclusive rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 292870.0,
      "end_time": 296600.0,
      "text": "for a month for streaming."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 296600.0,
      "end_time": 299441.0,
      "text": "So, that's one thing I\nwould've done differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 299441.0,
      "end_time": 301730.0,
      "text": "It ended up working out fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 301730.0,
      "end_time": 304430.0,
      "text": "- Then we talked about how\nhe got an intro to Netflix."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 305790.0,
      "end_time": 308770.0,
      "text": "- [Matt] So it was Gather\nwas the third-party company"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 310328.0,
      "end_time": 312560.0,
      "text": "So we had like, they then found"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 312560.0,
      "end_time": 314920.0,
      "text": "another company that was\nworking with Netflix."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 314920.0,
      "end_time": 316820.0,
      "text": "So that's how it worked out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 316820.0,
      "end_time": 321820.0,
      "text": "And very far removed from me who made it."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 321980.0,
      "end_time": 325540.0,
      "text": "So it was like three or\nfour steps of connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 325540.0,
      "end_time": 327060.0,
      "text": "- If you want that full\nepisode, and you wanna hear"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 327060.0,
      "end_time": 329040.0,
      "text": "the whole conversation with Matt D'Avella"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 329040.0,
      "end_time": 331320.0,
      "text": "that is down in the description below."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
